title: Eatin' on the Cuff or the Moth Who Came to Dinner

sources.title: Eatin' on the Cuff or the Moth Who Came to Dinner (1942)
sources.description: Eatin’ on the Cuff or The Moth Who Came to Dinner is a 1942 Looney Tunes short directed by Bob Clampett. Watch on RetroFlix.org:  https://retroflix.org/eatin-on-the-cuff-or-the-moth-who-came-to-dinner-1942/

metadata.Plot: A live-action piano player relates the story of the Moth who, on his way to marry his Honey Bee, falls into the clutches of an amourous black widow spider, who at one point disguises herself as Veronica Lake in an attempt to snare her man, er, bug.
metadata.Actors: Mel Blanc, Elvia Allman, Sara Berner
